"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-07-30-pollution-river-seine-forces-postponement-paris-olympics-triathlon-21323398\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"To view this video please enable JavaScript, and consider upgrading to a web \\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tbrowser thatsupports HTML5 \\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tvideo  Up Next  The men's triathlon at the ParisOlympicshas been postponed with pollution levels in the Seine still too high.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 244, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 33, \"end\": 43, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/JavaScript\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.336337461625917e-14, \"text\": \"JavaScript\", \"types\": [\"Q9143\", \"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/JavaScript\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/JavaScript\"}, {\"begin\": 105, \"end\": 110, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HTML5\", \"score\": 0.9999999900196599, \"rank\": 9.98037324811869e-09, \"text\": \"HTML5\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HTML5\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/HTML5\"}, {\"begin\": 223, \"end\": 228, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.9999999996346105, \"rank\": 3.615705861211831e-10, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Despite the improvement of water quality levels over the last hours, the readings at some points of the swim course are still above the acceptable limits,' read a statement from World Triathlon.\", \"from\": 246, \"to\": 441, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 425, \"end\": 440, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Triathlon\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.372391734413312e-15, \"text\": \"World Triathlon\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Triathlon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Triathlon\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Paris2024 and World Triathlon reiterate that their priority is the health of the athletes.'\", \"from\": 443, \"to\": 535, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Training sessions had been scheduled to take place on both Sunday and Mondaybut the filthy water resulted in two cancellations.\", \"from\": 537, \"to\": 664, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Organisers, who blamed a deluge of wet weatherduring Friday's opening ceremonyfor the worsening conditions, had been optimistic that conditions would improve and that competitive racing would go ahead as planned.\", \"from\": 666, \"to\": 878, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Metro.co.uk's live blog for updates from the Paris 2024 Olympics  Should levels of bacteria remain too high by Wednesday morning both the men's and women's races are likely to be postponed to Friday, the contingency day reserved for the events.\", \"from\": 880, \"to\": 1131, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If by Friday the water quality is still not good enough the swim leg will be scrapped and athletes will compete in a duathlon instead.\", \"from\": 1133, \"to\": 1267, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For the mixed triathlon relay event on August 5, the contingency day is August 6.\", \"from\": 1269, \"to\": 1350, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris authorities have promised to make the Seine swimmable as a key legacy of the Games, and spent 1.4 billion euros on wastewater infrastructure to contain sewage and minimise spillage into the waterway.\", \"from\": 1352, \"to\": 1557, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1352, \"end\": 1357, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999988631, \"rank\": 1.2464221038896258e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1396, \"end\": 1401, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.9999999996346105, \"rank\": 3.615705861211831e-10, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris Mayor Anne Hidalgo took a dip in the river herself earlier this month, in a bid to convince doubters.\", \"from\": 1559, \"to\": 1666, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1559, \"end\": 1570, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/List_of_mayors_of_Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Mayor\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/List_of_mayors_of_Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/List_of_mayors_of_Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1571, \"end\": 1583, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anne_Hidalgo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Anne Hidalgo\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anne_Hidalgo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anne_Hidalgo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The gamble that the river would be clean enough on the day of the triathlon was never guaranteed to pay off, especially as water quality varies widely day-to-day.\", \"from\": 1668, \"to\": 1830, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Rain significantly increases concentrations of infection-causing bacteria like E. coli and enterococci.\", \"from\": 1832, \"to\": 1935, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Seth Rider, one of 55 triathletes entered in the men's race, has told reporters he took unconventional measures to prepare for exposure to bacteria.\", \"from\": 1937, \"to\": 2085, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'We know that there is going to be some E. coli exposure, so I just try to increase my E. coli threshold by exposing myself to a bit of E. coli in your day-to-day life,' the U.S. athlete said in a press conference on Saturday.\", \"from\": 2087, \"to\": 2313, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ArrowMORE:Olympics schedule and results: France's Leon Marchand lights up Paris Olympics with two golds in one night  Arro